Generate the user upload option to upload compounds and their physical-chemical data

fileInput_UploadedComps.Rd

Generate the user upload option to upload compounds and their physical-chemical data

Usage

fileInput_UploadedComps(id)

Arguments

id

Shiny identifier name

Value

A browser and file upload box

See also

CS_UploadedData(), which calls the current function

Examples

fileInput_UploadedComps("file1")
